    (coordinateProcess X) (coordinateProcess Y) D1 D2 RX RY L1 L2 L3 M3 hL3 h𝓕 hSigma
  · exact lindeberg_integral_telescope (Ω := Ω) (mΩ := mΩ) μ f X Y hIntInterp
